#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-27B-Qwen3.6-27B.md:1
msgid "Qwen3.5-27B/Qwen3.6-27B"
msgstr "Qwen3.5-27B / Qwen3.6-27B"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-27B-Qwen3.6-27B.md:3
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-27B-Qwen3.6-27B.md:5
msgid ""
"Qwen3.5 and Qwen3.6-27B are dense models (not MoE) that share the same "
"hybrid attention design (GDN + full attention). Deployment on vLLM Ascend"
" follows the same pattern for both; only model weights, context length "
"defaults, and first-supported versions differ."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3.5 和 Qwen3.6-27B 是密集模型（非 MoE），共享相同的混合注意力设计（GDN + 全注意力）。在 vLLM Ascend "
"上的部署对两者遵循相同的模式；仅模型权重、上下文长度默认值和首次支持的版本有所不同。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-27B-Qwen3.6-27B.md:7
msgid ""
"Qwen3.5 represents a significant leap forward in multimodal learning, "
"architectural efficiency, and global accessibility. Qwen3.6-27B builds on"
" that architecture with stronger agentic coding, native multimodal "
"support, and up to 262144 context length."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3.5 在多模态学习、架构效率和全球可访问性方面代表了重大飞跃。Qwen3.6-27B 在此基础上构建，具有更强的智能体编码能力、原生多模态支持以及高达 262144 的上下文长度。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-27B-Qwen3.6-27B.md:9
msgid ""
"This document covers supported features, environment setup, single-node "
"deployment, and accuracy/performance evaluation."
msgstr "本文档涵盖支持的特性、环境设置、单节点部署以及精度/性能评估。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3.5-27B-Qwen3.6-27B.md:11
msgid "`Qwen3.5-27B` is first supported in `vllm-ascend:v0.17.0rc1`."
msgstr "`Qwen3.5-27B` 首次在 `vllm-ascend:v0.17.0rc1` 版本中得到支持。"

